      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;xv6的存储&#34;&gt;xv6的存储&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#xv6%e7%9a%84%e5%ad%98%e5%82%a8&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
